>> time required: 24 hours
>> course: side

Slice @cucumbers{2%large} into thick slices and cover with @salt{1%tbsp} for ~{30%minutes}
Rince cucumbers and pat dry
Mix @rice vinegar{3%tbsp}, @mirin{1.5%tbsp}, @sugar{2%tbsp}, @sesame oil{1.5%tbsp}, @garlic cloves{3}. 
Toss the cucumbers in the dressing and let sit for ~{24%hours} before serving

